m setting\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans are welcome to watch and wave at their favorite teams from the riverbank as they are paraded one-by-one in boats.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"their favorite teams\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"the riverbank\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"boats\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the inaugural celebration, global designers have prepared uniforms for each team, sharing intriguing sneak peeks online to generate excitement.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the inaugural celebration\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"global designers\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"uniforms\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"each team\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"intriguing sneak peeks\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since 2008,Team USA has tapped Ralph Laurento be the creator of their Olympic attire.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999992519406, \"rank\": 5.472529005119868e-10, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ralph Laurento\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"the creator\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic attire\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, the brand paid homage to the nation's existing patriotism with the teams opening ceremony outfits.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngra