ompetitors will don ivory trousers with a blue, red, and gold deels.\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Male competitors\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"ivory trousers\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"a blue, red, and gold deels\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Celestial drawings and animal symbols from the country's folklore are subtly stitched throughout.\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Celestial drawings\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"animal symbols\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's folklore\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both male and female athletes have two looks to choose from, while the Mongolian flag bearers will be dressed in their own unique garments, including buryats and gutals.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2703, \"end\": 2712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\", \"score\": 0.8965998433621515, \"rank\": 0.11508567421436455, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both male and female athletes\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"two looks\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"their own unique garments\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2770}, {\"ngram\": \"buryats\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"gutals\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Czech Republic Blue-blotted plastic trenches will dressTeam Czech Republicon July 26.\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2809, \"end\": 2817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.8064432562273838, \"rank\": 0.2400128428265434, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wik